{"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib\/DateTimeRef\/getWeekOfYear()","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"metadata":{"modules":[{"name":"GLib"}],"fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"getWeekOfYear"},{"text":"() -> ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"Int","preciseIdentifier":"s:Si"}],"roleHeading":"Instance Method","title":"getWeekOfYear()","extendedModule":"GLib","role":"symbol","externalID":"s:4GLib16DateTimeProtocolPAAE13getWeekOfYearSiyF::SYNTHESIZED::s:4GLib11DateTimeRefV","symbolKind":"method"},"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/glib\/datetimeref\/getweekofyear()"]}],"sections":[],"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib","doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib\/DateTimeRef","doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib\/DateTimeRef\/DateTimeProtocol-Implementations"]]},"kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"text":"Returns the ISO 8601 week number for the week containing ","type":"text"},{"code":"datetime","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":".","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"The ISO 8601 week number is the same for every day of the week (from"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"Moday through Sunday).  That can produce some unusual results"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"(described below)."}],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"getWeekOfYear"},{"text":"() -> ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:Si","text":"Int"}],"languages":["swift"],"platforms":["macOS"]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"text":"Discussion","type":"heading","level":2,"anchor":"discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The first week of the year is week 1.  This is the week that contains"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"the first Thursday of the year.  Equivalently, this is the first week","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"that has more than 4 of its days falling within the calendar year.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The value 0 is never returned by this function.  Days contained","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"within a year but occurring before the first ISO 8601 week of that"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"year are considered as being contained in the last week of the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"previous year.  Similarly, the final days of a calendar year may be"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"considered as being part of the first ISO 8601 week of the next year","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"if 4 or more days of that week are contained within the new year.","type":"text"}]}]}],"references":{"doc://GLib/documentation/GLib":{"kind":"symbol","role":"collection","abstract":[],"identifier":"doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib","title":"GLib","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/glib"},"doc://GLib/documentation/GLib/DateTimeRef/getWeekOfYear()":{"role":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/glib\/datetimeref\/getweekofyear()","title":"getWeekOfYear()","kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Returns the ISO 8601 week number for the week containing "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"datetime"},{"text":".","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"The ISO 8601 week number is the same for every day of the week (from"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"Moday through Sunday).  That can produce some unusual results","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"(described below)."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib\/DateTimeRef\/getWeekOfYear()","fragments":[{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"ident